  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So this was the hierarchy in Auschwitz, you see?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And these people, they already had a infrastructure built for themselves, supported by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Because you have to understand, you know, which I understood later, that there was tremendous amount of money that-- and jewelry that people were able to get ahold of from the transports that came into Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And because some prisoners-- there was a group called Canada.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And it was an odd name, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Why they called it Canada, because they thought that Canada is a country with such tremendous wealth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And this group, Canada, was the one that had to empty all the transport wagons after the people were taken out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They had to take out everything, and take it to a place, and search out every piece, because in bread, you know, people used to hide some money or something.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they had to open up every tube of toothpaste to see whether people were not hiding some diamonds or stuff like that in it, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So-- finished?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
